      <title>英国经济衰退以封锁结束以来最强劲的增长结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/uk-says-recession-ended-with-stronger-than-expected-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国经济从去年年底的浅度衰退中强劲反弹，这让迄今为止一直在努力兑现重振增长承诺的首相里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)松了一口气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/uk-says-recession-ended-with-stronger-than-expected-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
